<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>The Putting Method — Hero Prototype</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --page-bg: #07140F;
    --hero-bg: #0D1C15;
    --surface: #12231A;
    --raised: #1A2D22;
    --accent: #D7B76D;
    --accent-secondary: #8FA77A;
    --text-primary: #F5F1E7;
    --text-secondary: #C9C2B4;
    --text-muted: #879084;
    --border: #263A30;
    --accent-border: rgba(215, 183, 109, 0.30);
    --nav-bg: #FFFDF8;
    --nav-text: #07140F;
    --paper: var(--page-bg);
    --paper-2: var(--hero-bg);
    --ink: var(--nav-text);
    --muted: var(--text-muted);
    --forest: var(--page-bg);
    --forest-2: var(--hero-bg);
    --fairway: var(--accent-secondary);
    --brass: var(--accent);
    --sand: var(--text-secondary);
    --line: var(--border);
    --white: var(--text-primary);
    --shadow: 0 30px 100px rgba(7, 20, 15, 0.46), 0 12px 42px rgba(7, 20, 15, 0.34);
    --type-nav: 13px;
    --type-brand-kicker: 10px;
    --type-eyebrow: 12px;
    --type-hero: clamp(48px, 6.6vw, 86px);
    --type-lead: clamp(18px, 1.75vw, 22px);
    --type-button: 14px;
    --type-proof: 11px;
    --type-card-title: 18px;
    --type-card-body: 14px;
    --space-1: 8px;
    --space-2: 12px;
    --space-3: 16px;
    --space-4: 20px;
    --space-5: 24px;
    --space-6: 32px;
    --space-7: 40px;
    --space-8: 56px;
    --space-9: 72px;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% -12%, rgba(215, 183, 109, 0.16), transparent 32rem),
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(143, 167, 122, 0.18), transparent 30rem),
      var(--page-bg);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  body::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: .32;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(215, 183, 109, 0.045) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(215, 183, 109, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 42px 42px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, transparent 82%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  body::after {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: auto -8vw -28vh -8vw;
    height: 46vh;
    pointer-events: none;
    background:
      repeating-radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(143, 167, 122, .14) 0 2px, transparent 2px 18px);
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
    opacity: .45;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .site {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    background: var(--page-bg);
  }

  .nav {
    width: min(1220px, calc(100vw - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--nav-bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(7, 20, 15, 0.12);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 100vmax var(--nav-bg);
    clip-path: inset(0 -100vmax);
  }

  .brand {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--nav-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 750;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  .brand-mark {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--page-bg), var(--hero-bg));
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-border), 0 10px 24px rgba(7, 20, 15, .18);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: -0.08em;
  }

  .brand small {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 2px;
    color: rgba(7,20,15,.62);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: var(--type-brand-kicker);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--type-nav);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(7,20,15,.72);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-cta {
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--accent) !important;
    background: var(--page-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(7,20,15,.18);
  }

  .hero {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-9);
    background: var(--hero-bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
  }

  .device-stage {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: clamp(16px, 2vw, 24px) 0 var(--space-5);
  }

  .device-stage::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: min(940px, 78vw);
    height: 220px;
    bottom: 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(7,20,15,.55), rgba(7,20,15,0) 70%);
    filter: blur(20px);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .phone {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: min(1120px, 94vw);
    aspect-ratio: 2.26 / 1;
    padding: clamp(14px, 2.2vw, 28px);
    border-radius: clamp(38px, 5.5vw, 78px);
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--raised) 0%, var(--page-bg) 38%, var(--surface) 100%);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow), inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(255,255,255,.08), inset 0 -10px 28px rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    transform: perspective(1400px) rotateX(2deg);
  }

  .phone::before,
  .phone::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--raised), var(--page-bg));
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }

  .phone::before {
    left: 10px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 84px;
  }

  .phone::after {
    right: 18px;
    width: clamp(8px, 1vw, 12px);
    height: clamp(8px, 1vw, 12px);
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, var(--border), var(--page-bg) 70%);
  }

  .phone-screen {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: clamp(26px, 3.6vw, 48px);
    background: var(--page-bg);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-border), inset 0 0 44px rgba(255,255,255,.035);
  }

  .phone-screen::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 8px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 110px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--surface);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.08), 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    z-index: 2;
    opacity: .78;
  }

  .tempo-frame {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
    background: var(--page-bg);
  }

  .hero-copy {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px) auto 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: var(--type-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .eyebrow::before,
  .eyebrow::after {
    content: "";
    width: 38px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent-border);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-3);
    font-size: var(--type-hero);
    line-height: .96;
    letter-spacing: -0.068em;
    font-weight: 820;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-copy p {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--type-lead);
    line-height: 1.52;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }

  .btn {
    appearance: none;
    border: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 52px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-5);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: var(--type-button);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    color: var(--page-bg);
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(7,20,15,.30);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    background: var(--raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(7,20,15,.22);
  }

  .proof-row {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .proof-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-1);
    padding: 9px 13px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(18, 35, 26, .78);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: var(--type-proof);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .02em;
  }

  .proof-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(215,183,109,.16);
  }

  .next-section {
    width: min(1060px, calc(100vw - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-9);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: 30px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .next-card {
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: var(--raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .next-card span {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    color: var(--brass);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: var(--type-eyebrow);
  }

  .next-card h3 {
    margin: var(--space-2) 0 var(--space-1);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: var(--type-card-title);
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  .next-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-size: var(--type-card-body);
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .nav { height: 72px; width: min(100vw - 28px, 1220px); }
    .nav-links a:not(.nav-cta) { display: none; }
    .brand small { display: none; }
    .phone { width: 1080px; max-width: calc(100vw - 18px); padding: 10px; border-radius: 38px; transform: none; }
    .phone-screen { border-radius: 28px; }
    .phone-screen::before { width: 72px; height: 14px; top: 5px; }
    .hero { padding-top: var(--space-5); }
    .hero-copy { margin-top: var(--space-6); }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(42px, 12vw, 58px); }
    .next-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .hero { width: 100%; }
    .phone { aspect-ratio: 1.95 / 1; }
    .hero-actions { align-items: stretch; }
    .btn { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="site">
    <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="The Putting Method home">
        <span class="brand-mark">PM</span>
        <span>The Putting Method<small>Line · Speed · Tempo · Proof</small></span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links" aria-label="Main links">
        <a href="#trainer">Trainer</a>
        <a href="#method">Method</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="#start">Start training</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main id="top" class="hero">
      <section class="device-stage" id="trainer" aria-label="Tempo Trainer preview in landscape phone">
        <div class="phone" aria-label="Landscape phone showing the Tempo Trainer app">
          <div class="phone-screen">
            <iframe class="tempo-frame" title="Interactive Putting Tempo Trainer" src="https://ccsedge.github.io/Putting-App/"></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="hero-copy" aria-label="Hero message">
        <div class="eyebrow">Train the part of golf everyone can master</div>
        <h1>Every golfer can putt like an elite player.</h1>
        <p>You do not need tour-level speed, strength, or athleticism to become dangerous on the greens. You need a measurable system for start line, speed, tempo, green reading, and pressure — then a way to prove the work is lowering your score.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#start">Build my putting baseline</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#method">See the system</a>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-row" aria-label="Platform highlights">
          <span class="proof-pill"><span class="proof-dot"></span>14-day trial · no credit card</span>
          <span class="proof-pill"><span class="proof-dot"></span>Tempo · green reading · strokes gained</span>
          <span class="proof-pill"><span class="proof-dot"></span>Built for practice and the course</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <section class="next-section" id="method" aria-label="Method preview">
      <article class="next-card">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Calibrate the stroke</h3>
        <p>Use the landscape trainer to pair stroke length, capture speed, stimp, slope, grain, and break before practice starts.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="next-card">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Diagnose the leak</h3>
        <p>Track misses by distance, break type, and result so practice is based on evidence instead of frustration.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="next-card">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Prescribe the work</h3>
        <p>Turn the miss pattern into focused drills, warm-up blocks, and a roadmap that keeps putting simple.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
